item.title: About
item.description: About me You probably know me as lambda-λ, I am an Electrical Engineering student at KFU, and a self taught Software Engineer. I live in an ivory tower where I know that I know nothing. I code (but suck at coding) in Rust, Haskell (Still learning!) and Typescript (But forgot!). Use Artix Linux and enjoy $\LaTeX$ (yep, I loaded an entire js library just for rendering that word)! In case you are wondering, no this isn’t my main blog, this is just for college related stuff.
